    BUG FIX — item_subscription.xml references @drawable/ic_app_placeholder
    as the default src for the subscription logo ImageView. This drawable did
    not exist in the project, causing an inflate crash whenever the RecyclerView
    tried to render a row.

    This is a simple grey circle that acts as a neutral placeholder before
    any real logo is loaded.
-->
